\c 16
\s Nhaka yaEfuremu
\p
\v 1 Zvino kwakabuda mujenya wevana vaJosefa kubva paJoridhani paJeriko kusvika pamvura yeJeriko kumabvazuva, kurenje uchikwira kubva paJeriko panyika yezvikomo yeBheteri;
\v 2 ndokubuda kubva paBheteri kuenda kuRuzi, ndokupfuurira kumuganhu wevaArikiti kuAtaroti.
\v 3 Zvino wakaburukira nechekumavirazuva kumuganhu wevaJafireti kuenda kumuganhu weBheti-Horoni pazasi, uye kusvika kuGezeri; uye kubuda kwawo kwaiva pagungwa.
\v 4 Zvino vanakomana vaJosefa, Manase naEfuremu vakagara nhaka.
\p
\v 5 Zvino muganhu wevana vaEfuremu zvichienderana nemhuri dzavo waiva \add wakadai\add*: Iwo muganhu wenhaka yavo kumabvazuva waiva Ataroti-Adhari kusvika Bheti-Horoni kumusoro.
\v 6 Zvino muganhu wakabudira kugungwa paMikimetati kubva kumaodzanyemba; muganhu ndokudzokera kumabvazuva paTanati-Shiro, ndokupfuura napo kumabvazuva kuenda kuJanowa;
\v 7 zvino wakaburuka kubva paJanowa kuenda kuAtaroti nekuNahara, ndokugunzva Jeriko, ndokubudira paJoridhani.
\v 8 Kubva paTapua muganhu wakaenda kumavirazuva kurwizi Kana, uye kubuda kwawo kwaiva pagungwa. Iyi inhaka yerudzi rwevana vaEfuremu zvichienderana nemhuri dzavo.
\v 9 Uye maguta aiva akakamurirwa vana vaEfuremu aiva pakati penhaka yevana vaManase, maguta ose nemisha yawo.
\v 10 Zvino havana kudzinga VaKenani vaigara paGezeri. Naizvozvo VaKenani vakagara pakati peVaEfuremu kusvika nhasi; asi vakava vabati vechibharo.